dcterms:description: The Tab2Know dataset contains information regarding tables extracted from scientific papers in the Semantic Scholar Open Research Corpus. It includes 73k tables labeled using Snorkel, with a focus on classifying tables into four types: Observation, Input, Example, and Other.
